{"tid":1310032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[前事不忘] 勿忘警賊自導自演暴徒扔火 林鄭政府一早已經想製造暴徒","createTime":"2019-07-12T13:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T13:43:48.000Z","uid":78336,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"571fd991aa63c27569031f82847c1a40451468d4","tid":1310032,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:11:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MR.JackyHTLim/videos/2148060712152080/?s=751415228&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMR.JackyHTLim%2Fvideos%2F2148060712152080%2F%3Fs%3D751415228%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=b2daf442\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MR.JackyHTLim/videos/2148060712152080/?s=751415228&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n記唔記得係6月9號之前 撕紙狗已經開始想造暴徒扔火煲大件事<br />\n結果比人車cam影到 班狗就即刻潛水當無講過<br />\n呢件事入面 扔火暴徒影到衣著+車顏色<br />\n企定定係度等衝鋒車經過 衝鋒車都停係度等人扔<br />\n如果撕紙狗要捉人 香港周圍都係天眼 係附近逐個逐個睇cam一定捉到<br />\n但係到而家都無去告人<br />\n由6月7到6月12強行二讀<br />\n由到頭尾政府都一心一意想屈香港人係暴徒<br />\n然後開槍鎮壓 黎一次香港六四 換二十年平靜<br />\n希望大家追究612既同時 唔好唔記得追究埋呢件扔火案<br />\n狙擊香蕉糖可以QR Code送片 就唔爭在比埋呢條片既link香港市民睇<br />\n等大家見識下香港警賊係幾咁無恥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25b618c09eb78d94cf074e9684091eebf54ccc7","tid":1310032,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"屌 又開錯吹水台<br />\n連狗可唔可以幫我搬返去政事/時事台"},{"pid":"0c9d2337f1654747d95621c46aaf59802f5a46fa","tid":1310032,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1920365e6b0761ec72133eaf8bc01d387042579c","tid":1310032,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:12:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2aba1fbe53df2da4e15e39c8c46663add6960968","tid":1310032,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2